          "reviewBody": "I wish I could give it a 0 star but I could no not do so .Everyone here is praising the school and giving it 5 stars etc But in my opinion it is the worst school in bhopal no no it is the worst in India actually, it is the worst school in the world which is ever known to mankind .I will give reasons\n1. Very very bad infrastructure\n2. Very bad fees structure ( FEES IS NOT WORTH IT )\n3. Students are always abusing no matter what the topic is.\n4. Teachers doing gender discrimination\n5. Students trying to be DON of the school\n6. School assembly is the worst (we have to stand for 1 hrs straight in the blazing hot sun )\n7. The last ,the prefects think that they could do anything like beating the students , making them stand in the last row in the assembly for no reason etc etc .\n\nI HAVE MUCH MORE COMPLAINTS BUT IF I START WRITING THEM MY HAND WOULD BE IN UNBEARABLE PAIN!!!\n\nTHE SCHOOL IS VERY BAD AND NEEDS IMPROVEMENT ASAP!!!",
